reviews.text: Didnt give 5 stars only because nothing is perfect.

Lovely little bar, 60s music. Trendy and cool

Love it!

This bar is legendary when the bartender Neil locks the lively late-night clientele in for an evening of fun, free shots and entertaining banter - lucky if you land the back-room sofas and dart-board for a more personal engagement with friends. A very staple local for the night-owls of KTown.
A great bar with friendly staff and patrons. Really enjoy the nights we have had here. Make sure you ask about the pen marks on the mirror
Lovely Staff
